## âœ¨ Features

- ğŸ¨ **No-Code**: Pure YAML configurationâ€”no scripting required
- ğŸ”„ **Composable**: Reusable components and multi-step workflows
- ğŸš€ **Production Ready**: HTTP/MCP servers + Web UI + Docker deployment
- ğŸ”Œ **Connect Anything**: External AI services, local models, vector stores, and more
- âš¡ **Stream & Scale**: Real-time streaming and event-driven automation
- âš™ï¸ **Configuration**: Environment variables, flexible settings
- ğŸ”— **Integration**: Webhooks, tunneling, HTTP servers

